---
title: Creamy Chicken Penne with Parmesan & Greens
description: This saucy creation uses a creamy tomato sauce to coat penne, with chunks of tender chicken and flavoursome Parmesan. Add baby spinach leaves that gently wilts when tossed with the pasta, and you’ve got a new recipe that's sure to please everyone.
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/creamy-chicken-penne-df3e5c0f.jpg
